Justification for Mapping: First indicator 0: Devices, equipment, or software required to implement an accessibility feature (from MARC Manual) -- ZP 12/26/2022

First indicator 8: Could be any combination of accessibility content, deficiencies or technical requirements; mapped to a general note -- ZP 12/26/2022

Transformation Notes: Append "(Applies to: + {value of $3})" to the end of string
